headline: Aflac Gears Up for Q2 Earnings: Ready to Quack or Set to Crack?
summary: AFL braces for Q2 results with EPS likely to decline 6.6% and revenue off 13.7% as U.S. and Japan earnings face pressure.

headline: LevelBlue Completes Acquisition of Aon’s Cybersecurity and IP Litigation Consulting Groups
summary: DALLAS & DUBLIN, August 01, 2025--LevelBlue, a global leader in cloud-based, AI-driven managed security services, today announced the completion of its acquisition of Aon’s (NYSE: AON) Cybersecurity and Intellectual Property (IP) Litigation consulting groups, including the renowned cybersecurity firm, Stroz Friedberg, and Elysium Digital. With this completion the consulting group will operate as Stroz Friedberg, a LevelBlue company.
